  "body": "# **USE WITH EMF 3.1.1!**\n\n![VN4 Presents](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/78f6ab45cfab60dceefdb9b8be5507383e19b622.png)\n![FWS](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/79134d8427d3afb3d8af46be9db9947c11909412.png)\n# \nThis pack brings the Fresh Animations to Cracker's Wither Storm mod, along with other various features.\n# \n# <center><Page is being reworked></center>\n![Features](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/2b8cc84b888731091927cabf4fd0b51a52e8b577.png)\n<details>\n<summary>Full list:</summary>\n\n## Fresh Wither Storm features:\n- Fresh Animations compatibility for Sickened Mobs from Cracker's Wither Storm Mod.\n- Custom sounds for pigs with the name reuben when using ESF.\n### Available with CWSM and Custom models.\n## Reanimated Wither Storm features:\n- Custom menu panorama.\n- Wither and Wither Storm spawn animations.\n- Flaming Wither Skull fire texture animation when using MoreMcMeta.\n- Bowels Tentacle entity animations.\n- Bowels Wither Storm Head entity animations.\n- Wither Storm tentacle animations.\n- Custom extensions located inside the file (Alternatives).\n### Available with CWSM and Custom models.\n## Fresh + Reanimated Wither Storm features:\n- All of FWS and RWS features.\n### Available with CWSM and Custom models.\n</details>\n\n#\n![requirements](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/c490cc2d0edf694f5c004278148669b2b8880cb2.png)\n<center>\n  <table>\n   <tr>\n     <td>\n       Project\n     </td>\n     <td>\n       Fresh Wither Storm\n     </td>\n     <td>\n       Reanimated Wither Storm\n     </td>\n     <td>\n       Fresh + Reanimated Wither Storm\n     </td>\n   </tr>\n   <tr>\n     <td>\n         <img alt=\"CWSM\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/00352ff4c745fe53300282da40481c7961f54643_0.webp\">\n     </td>\n     <td>\n         <img alt=\"REQUIRED\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/a938f3e5fce57a0acaa60fd7e1e34b2b31d65e43_0.webp\">\n     </td>\n     <td>\